------
Gevent
------

http://www.gevent.org/
A coroutine-based Python networking library that uses greenlet to provide a high-level synchronous API on top of libevent event loop.

Docs: http://www.gevent.org/contents.html
Addons: http://code.google.com/p/gevent/wiki/ProjectsUsingGevent
Benchmark: http://nichol.as/benchmark-of-python-web-servers


Installation:

yum install libevent-devel
easy_install gevent

	
------------
Gevent-MySQL
------------

https://github.com/mthurlin/gevent-MySQL
Asynchronous mysql driver from Concurrence adapted to gevent

Installation:
	
easy_install cython
git clone https://github.com/mthurlin/gevent-MySQL.git gevent-MySQL
cd gevent-MySQL && python setup.py install


